Follow the instructions in:
https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/setup/linux#_visual-studio-code-is-unable-to-watch-for-file-changes-in-this-large-workspace-error-enospc

Or:
Download: https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=760868
Increase inotify because some of the repos I have have a huge number of files:
fs.inotify.max_user_watches=524288
sudo sysctl -p

In extensions install:
Code Runner
GitLens
One Dark Pro
PHP IntelliSense
phpfmt

In settings:
Change Editor: Render White Space to all
Workbench: Color Theme to One Dark Pro